Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.15,0:00:10.99,Default,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}In Use
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.12,0:01:47.57,Default,Doc,0000,0000,0000,,Her injuries are minor,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.57,0:01:49.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so the pain should \Nsubside relatively quickly,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.77,0:01:51.63,Default,Doc,0000,0000,0000,,but she should avoid strenuous activities.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.20,0:01:53.00,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.58,0:01:56.73,Default,Doc,0000,0000,0000,,Also, I noticed signs of malnutrition.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.52,0:01:59.09,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Malnutrition?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.09,0:02:01.05,Default,Doc,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know why that would be?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.98,0:02:04.01,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.13,0:02:16.52,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,You'll have to withdraw from the tournament.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.22,0:02:19.81,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,They asked that you not participate
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.81,0:02:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,because they can't be responsible \Nfor a minor getting hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.14,0:02:28.43,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,You've caused a lot of trouble for everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.43,0:02:29.67,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,You need to take a step back.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.69,0:02:39.43,Default,Title,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 8 \NWorrying and Racing Ahead
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.22,0:02:46.25,Default,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't been eating much lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.50,0:02:48.68,Default,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.10,0:02:52.03,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never get in...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.68,0:02:54.79,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,There's a weight limit,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.79,0:02:57.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and they won't take anyone who's over it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.10,0:02:59.42,Default,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,At the equestrian school?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.88,0:03:00.71,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.36,0:03:03.57,Default,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,What's the limit?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.68,0:03:07.81,Default,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.28,0:03:11.12,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I lose weight,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.12,0:03:12.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there's a parent interview.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.43,0:03:16.69,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,And if I get any taller, \Nit'll totally ruin my chances.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.88,0:03:19.13,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,When I called them,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.80,0:03:21.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they were completely discouraging.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.39,0:03:26.06,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,It's not my fault I'm tall!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.58,0:03:28.10,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,I told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.51,0:03:30.13,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,You got yourself here because
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.13,0:03:33.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you were stuck in your dream \Nworld, ignoring basic facts!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.31,0:03:34.02,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.02,0:03:35.88,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Can you see how naive you've been?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.88,0:03:37.42,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,I'll pay for your education,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.42,0:03:39.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so study and go to university.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.18,0:03:41.60,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Once you have a career,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.60,0:03:42.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you can ride in your free time—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.99,0:03:44.01,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Shut up, shut up, shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.01,0:03:45.43,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.92,0:03:49.01,Default,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.37,0:04:08.92,Default,Teach,0000,0000,0000,,You'll face a few problems,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.92,0:04:10.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,changing your plan this late,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.54,0:04:11.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but there's no rush.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.91,0:04:13.27,Default,Teach,0000,0000,0000,,Take your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.32,0:04:24.74,Default,paper,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}1st Choice: Riding Academy
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.32,0:04:24.74,Default,paper,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}2nd Choice: Nothing <3
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.07,0:04:41.18,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Why are they using our room?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.84,0:04:43.56,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you know you have to audition
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.56,0:04:45.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to use the main stage \Nduring the White Festival?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.54,0:04:47.51,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,All music rooms are reserved as
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.51,0:04:49.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,practice rooms for those participants.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.92,0:04:52.75,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,We want to use this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.75,0:04:54.02,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,You can't just do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.55,0:04:57.06,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,We've got the vice principal's permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.06,0:04:58.82,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,And what about us?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.82,0:05:01.08,Default,Girl2,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure there's room for you by the bike rack.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.76,0:05:03.28,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,But there's no piano there!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.28,0:05:05.36,Default,Girl2,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you actually use one?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.36,0:05:07.87,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's in a mad scramble
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.87,0:05:10.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to secure practice rooms \Nbefore the festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.79,0:05:12.51,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,It's because you don't know this stuff
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.51,0:05:14.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that people think you're playing around.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.43,0:05:16.77,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Horseback riding does \Nnot constitute work.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.77,0:05:17.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's play!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.09,0:05:20.93,Default,Girl2,0000,0000,0000,,Must be nice to have \Nso much free time!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.93,0:05:21.71,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.16,0:05:24.72,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,And don't make me laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.25,0:05:27.57,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,What makes you so great, \Nwhen all you're doing
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.57,0:05:30.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is chugging down the tracks the \Nvice principal laid out for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.51,0:05:34.14,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Don't assume we're out of the running \Nbecause we didn't know about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.14,0:05:37.91,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,If you think too hard, \Nyou might hurt your little brains.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.91,0:05:38.56,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,Sawa...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.56,0:05:39.92,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,We're only getting started,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.92,0:05:41.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but you have the nerve to \Ntell me we have no chance?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.75,0:05:42.15,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.15,0:05:44.38,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it'll work out just fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.38,0:05:47.32,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Trying to take away our \None chance is so unfair!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.32,0:05:48.03,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,Sawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.64,0:05:55.54,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.92,0:06:10.53,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,You have a piano at home, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.53,0:06:14.01,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, but my room won't fit five people.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.66,0:06:16.26,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,The guys can stay outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.26,0:06:17.49,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.49,0:06:18.66,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be a brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.66,0:06:20.37,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Think about the times we had nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.91,0:06:22.31,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,We've got a piano at my place.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.09,0:06:24.39,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,There room for five people?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.39,0:06:25.38,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.38,0:06:26.79,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,And it'd be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.79,0:06:27.81,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,For sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.81,0:06:29.28,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,My parents aren't home in the afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.62,0:06:31.10,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Where do you live?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.10,0:06:32.66,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,About thirty minutes from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.66,0:06:34.62,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,I'll lead the way. We'll take the train.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.20,0:06:36.56,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.56,0:06:39.12,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Party at Wien's house!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.41,0:06:42.24,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,This is why people say \Nwe're just playing around.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.24,0:06:44.58,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,Would you rather she act \Nlike the vice principal?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.89,0:06:47.13,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,Sawa, we're leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.45,0:06:52.05,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, okay, I'll go grab my bike.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.05,0:06:53.77,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,But we're taking the train.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.44,0:06:56.66,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right. Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.18,0:07:04.52,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Lost love...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.15,0:07:10.03,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,Are you friends with any ninjas?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.03,0:07:10.91,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.91,0:07:12.77,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,They must be in hiding, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.77,0:07:15.02,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, does your \Nplace have high ceilings?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.70,0:07:19.29,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,I wish we could choose \Nwho we fall in love with...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.98,0:07:25.86,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,If we had a choice, \Nwe'd be spared a world of pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.31,0:07:32.09,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, if you end up with \Nthe person you want, that's great,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.09,0:07:34.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but plenty of people don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.70,0:07:35.83,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,It's so sad...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.41,0:07:37.77,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Konatsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.42,0:07:42.12,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,I know you'll find someone who loves you,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.12,0:07:43.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and who'll take care of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.71,0:07:44.27,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.98,0:07:48.09,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,But until that day, \Nif you need someone to hold,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.09,0:07:49.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you can hold me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.37,0:07:58.37,Default,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Maeda
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.47,0:08:04.25,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Your house has a gate!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.45,0:08:11.88,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Are you millionaires?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.20,0:08:16.66,Default,Wein,0000,0000,0000,,This used to be my grandfather's house,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.66,0:08:18.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but he donated it to the \Ncompany before he died.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.89,0:08:20.23,Default,Wein,0000,0000,0000,,Since we had to move so suddenly,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.23,0:08:21.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we're renting it for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.56,0:08:24.52,Default,Wein,0000,0000,0000,,We don't use most of the rooms.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.72,0:08:26.89,Default,Wein,0000,0000,0000,,This way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.75,0:08:29.53,Default,Wein,0000,0000,0000,,Come on in.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.13,0:08:34.85,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,This place is huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.85,0:08:35.91,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,There's even a fireplace.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.91,0:08:37.55,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, let's start a fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.55,0:08:38.55,Default,Wein,0000,0000,0000,,We can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.55,0:08:40.73,Default,Wein,0000,0000,0000,,It's not used anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.73,0:08:43.21,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,These would get in the \Nway of a badminton game.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.21,0:08:44.67,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,You can't play in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.67,0:08:46.31,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Sawa, check this out!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.31,0:08:47.97,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Death Chop!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.97,0:08:48.60,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.60,0:08:49.86,Default,Wein,0000,0000,0000,,Don't touch those!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.55,0:08:51.13,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.38,0:08:53.01,Default,Wein,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.62,0:08:56.97,Default,Wein,0000,0000,0000,,It's just, those are very important to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.97,0:08:58.76,Default,Wein,0000,0000,0000,,They're the Gambaraijers,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.76,0:09:00.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the heroes who protect the world's hopes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.91,0:09:04.86,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.86,0:09:05.98,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,The red one's missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.69,0:09:12.88,Default,Wein,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Red's on a very important \Nmission, in a faraway place.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.76,0:09:16.28,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,So, where's the piano?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.76,0:09:38.95,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,We can't use this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.95,0:09:41.07,Default,Wein,0000,0000,0000,,You guys came all the \Nway here for nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.07,0:09:41.99,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.99,0:09:44.64,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,We'll just practice without the piano.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.04,0:09:47.71,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, but I need to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.19,0:09:52.92,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,If your breakup was that painful, \Nyou should talk to us about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.92,0:09:53.78,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.78,0:09:56.53,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,We all want to help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.68,0:09:58.54,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,We do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.41,0:10:07.69,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,So, you can't be a jockey?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.88,0:10:10.94,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never get into the school.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.94,0:10:13.77,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,But that's not for sure, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.77,0:10:15.52,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe if you try really hard...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.52,0:10:16.29,Default,Wein,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.29,0:10:17.72,Default,Wein,0000,0000,0000,,You can do it, Sawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.91,0:10:22.05,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,What if you tried taking a step back?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.65,0:10:25.77,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,A step back?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.77,0:10:28.36,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, some distance might help you examine
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.36,0:10:30.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,your feelings with more clari—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.91,0:10:31.69,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Must be nice to be such an expert!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.89,0:10:36.95,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,You can only talk like that because \Nmusic is easy to go back to!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.40,0:10:40.95,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,But if I step back now, \Nit's all over for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.30,0:10:43.44,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have no future!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.93,0:10:45.95,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Sawa...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.52,0:10:49.98,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad I was able to \Ngo back to music,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.63,0:10:55.34,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,because my mother and I promised \Nto write a song together.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.88,0:10:59.88,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,Music keeps me connected to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.46,0:11:04.96,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,Then again, if I could see her \Njust one more time...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.94,0:11:08.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd give up music in a heartbeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.91,0:11:11.52,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,But that's not an option.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.58,0:11:28.95,Default,Book,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Even a Cat Can Learn
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.58,0:11:28.95,Default,Book,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Lessons in Composition
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.04,0:11:35.96,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,A cat's kicking my butt...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.45,0:11:44.64,Default,Phone,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Okita Sawa
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.94,0:12:04.28,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Stepping back just means quitting.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.64,0:12:07.82,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Why is everyone telling me to quit?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.34,0:12:11.62,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Am I being naive?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.76,0:12:17.62,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,I feel so empty...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.05,0:12:22.93,Default,Teach,0000,0000,0000,,It might sound strange,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.93,0:12:25.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but according to \Nvirtual water theory,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.39,0:12:29.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Japanese water supply is largely \Ndependent on foreign sources.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.88,0:12:32.01,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.67,0:12:34.98,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,You asked for us?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.37,0:12:39.78,Default,Vice,0000,0000,0000,,Withdraw your application.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.72,0:12:45.88,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.47,0:12:50.46,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,You're just favoring the \Nmusic majors over us,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.46,0:12:53.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,since they're more serious \Nabout the future, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.14,0:12:57.25,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,We respectfully refuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.61,0:13:02.52,Default,Vice,0000,0000,0000,,Sakai-san, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.52,0:13:04.78,Default,Vice,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't approve your \Nentry into general studies
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.78,0:13:07.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so you could waste your \Ntime on such nonsense.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.31,0:13:13.42,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,Until I entered the choir club,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.94,0:13:17.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought of music as a \Nskill you cultivated alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.55,0:13:21.03,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,But I was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.84,0:13:23.32,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,You need to be with others,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.32,0:13:26.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,let your feelings intersect and connect,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.81,0:13:29.33,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,and experience joy and suffering together.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.93,0:13:31.89,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not explaining it well, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.89,0:13:34.80,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,I can't create a beautiful harmony...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.80,0:13:36.70,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...all by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.70,0:13:38.21,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Isn't it more fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.80,0:13:40.67,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Isn't it nice to be around people?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.14,0:13:44.58,Default,Vice,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Despite what you said,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.58,0:13:47.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}you always went off and \Naccomplished things on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.05,0:13:55.22,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Madam Vice Principal, music does love me,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.22,0:13:56.52,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,if only a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.08,0:13:59.62,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Remember when you told me
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.62,0:14:03.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't have that special \Nsomething that moves people?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.64,0:14:06.17,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do it alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.17,0:14:07.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But with the help of my friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.94,0:14:09.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I'm finally at a point
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.22,0:14:12.03,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,where I have the potential \Nto move people's hearts.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.97,0:14:22.41,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,I believe a teacher's job \Nis to develop that potential!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.85,0:14:26.03,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,So please, let us go up on that stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.79,0:14:32.43,Default,Vice,0000,0000,0000,,All right, but you'll have to convince me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.88,0:14:34.73,Default,Vice,0000,0000,0000,,There's an audition for all groups who
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.73,0:14:36.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,wish to use the main stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.52,0:14:39.04,Default,Vice,0000,0000,0000,,Don't just tell me your \Nchoir club has improved.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.04,0:14:42.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prove it, by participating \Nin the audition.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.45,0:14:45.74,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,We will.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.74,0:14:47.07,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,When is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.28,0:14:48.21,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Today?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.90,0:14:52.65,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad. Very, very bad. Sawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.39,0:14:54.12,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}She's not here today, \Nwe'll have to go it alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.12,0:14:55.01,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Are you nuts?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.01,0:14:57.03,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,If we were a choir of 100,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.03,0:14:58.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,this would be like missing 20 people!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.89,0:15:02.74,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Why won't Sawa pick up her phone?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.74,0:15:03.95,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,Leave a message.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.95,0:15:05.07,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,I'll text her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.09,0:15:12.01,Default,Ans,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The customer you have dialed \Nis away from the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.01,0:15:14.99,Default,Ans,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Please leave a message after the beep.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.57,0:15:18.94,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Sawa, we're in trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.94,0:15:22.77,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,We just found out we have to \Naudition for the main stage, today!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.77,0:15:25.13,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Please come! If you leave now, \Nyou could make it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.13,0:15:27.22,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Without you, we'll be totally—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.28,0:15:46.07,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,She's not calling back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.07,0:15:46.92,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Let it go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.49,0:15:49.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's in no condition to sing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.05,0:15:50.30,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,He's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.52,0:15:53.04,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,That hurts...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.59,0:15:57.18,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,Sawa's really depressed, so maybe
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.18,0:15:59.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,saying "we want you here" isn't enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.92,0:16:01.87,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.68,0:16:06.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We should be doing something for {\i1}her...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.54,0:16:10.99,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,When I was depressed, \NI wanted to be left alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.84,0:16:14.97,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,Then again, it was nice to know people cared.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.81,0:16:19.00,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Then we have to somehow \Nshow Sawa that we care!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.94,0:16:22.11,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,But how?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.75,0:16:32.72,Default,From,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Sakai Wakana
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.94,0:16:25.66,Default,From,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't think I said anything horrible,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.66,0:16:27.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}or was told anything horrible that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.17,0:16:32.06,Default,From,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But if I hurt you in \Nany way, I apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.06,0:16:32.72,Default,From,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.62,0:16:35.25,Default,From,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Did you get Konatsu's message?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.75,0:16:38.83,Default,From,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We don't want to give up without a fight,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.83,0:16:40.30,Default,From,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}so the four of us are going to sing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.05,0:16:44.36,Default,From,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But we'd feel much more \Nconfident if you were with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.03,0:16:49.84,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Wakana is so strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.78,0:16:52.25,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Now I'm embarrassed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.75,0:16:54.99,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,I'm asking you to explain your reason!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.85,0:16:57.93,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,What? The parents' heights?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.93,0:16:59.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How is that relevant?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.95,0:17:02.78,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,What about a horse's \Nconnection with its rider?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.17,0:17:04.92,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,My daughter is serious about this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.52,0:17:07.52,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,She's been riding since she was a little girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.52,0:17:08.88,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,She can care for them, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.88,0:17:10.71,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,She's a gentle girl, who understands the
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.71,0:17:12.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,hearts of horses better than anyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.66,0:17:13.42,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.78,0:17:15.38,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,I dare you to say that again!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.79,0:17:17.21,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,You're dealing with a monk, here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.21,0:17:19.51,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,I'll send you straight to hell! Bam!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.62,0:17:22.02,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,My daughter's been through hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.76,0:17:24.62,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,She's been so worried,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.62,0:17:26.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she went on a ridiculous diet
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.40,0:17:28.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that made her fall off her horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.46,0:17:29.36,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.20,0:17:31.50,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,She's serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.50,0:17:36.36,Default,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what he says, \Nyou mean the world to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.20,0:17:41.38,Default,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,He's just terrible at expressing his feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.38,0:17:44.96,Default,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,I'll talk to the school.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.96,0:17:48.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should apologize to your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.29,0:17:49.50,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.90,0:17:58.04,Default,Ask,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Please leave a message after the beep.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.68,0:18:01.11,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sawa, are you listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.11,0:18:03.31,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I only have one thing to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.31,0:18:05.30,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I care about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.30,0:18:08.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll always be here for \Nyou, if you'll let me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.55,0:18:09.80,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And we're still waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.80,0:18:11.02,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's two things.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.93,0:18:14.64,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Anyway, Miyamoto Konatsu will now sing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.51,0:18:21.43,Default,Song,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I believe in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.43,0:18:25.82,Default,Song,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sawa, I'll wait for you forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.82,0:18:26.46,Default,Song,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.46,0:18:27.60,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.14,0:18:34.37,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}With the courage to accept \Nwhat can't be changed,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.37,0:18:38.86,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}you'll move forward again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.86,0:18:39.73,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.40,0:18:41.79,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.79,0:18:46.75,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even if you stumble, \Neven if you lose a match,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.75,0:18:50.70,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}there's always tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.04,0:18:51.90,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.10,0:18:57.56,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The light of hope burns \Nbright forevermore,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.56,0:19:04.21,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}because you are a hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.21,0:19:06.82,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's right, you're a hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.03,0:19:09.90,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Sawa, that was our—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.90,0:19:11.63,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What a weird song.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.63,0:19:12.58,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,You were listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.85,0:19:15.71,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Yep, I was.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.71,0:19:17.70,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We're in big trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.70,0:19:19.45,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The vice principal said we have to—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.45,0:19:20.50,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.09,0:19:24.16,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,I'm on my way, so wait right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.95,0:19:30.10,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But we're taking the train.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.10,0:19:31.72,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh, right. Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.72,0:19:51.71,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,I'm off!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.32,0:19:54.77,Default,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, see you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.95,0:20:02.68,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Must be our turn soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.82,0:20:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Think Sawa will make it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.39,0:20:08.59,Default,Ann,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}Choir club, please get ready.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.98,0:20:10.56,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,We're first?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.10,0:20:13.72,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,I wish we could've all been here for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.72,0:20:15.31,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,I've got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.31,0:20:17.73,Default,Button,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Push in Case of Emergency
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.86,0:20:19.32,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.32,0:20:21.86,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,If this isn't an emergency, \Nthen what is?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.86,0:20:24.48,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Not this, that's for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.48,0:20:27.24,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Forget the festival, \Nour club will be disbanded!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.44,0:20:29.59,Default,Ann,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}Vice principal, there is a call for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.59,0:20:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}Please come to the telephone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.00,0:20:34.93,Default,Ann,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}Vice principal, there is a call for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.93,0:20:37.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}Please come to the telephone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.38,0:20:39.41,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Was that you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.84,0:21:00.33,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Please hurry, Sabure!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.86,0:21:04.28,Default,Ann,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}Vice principal, there is a call for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.28,0:21:06.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}Please come to the telephone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.21,0:21:30.00,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.76,0:21:46.86,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,I made it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.86,0:21:47.91,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.26,0:23:31.74,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,I like red.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.74,0:23:33.51,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,Are we really wearing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.51,0:23:35.77,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Bursting with flavor! Whitebait White!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.77,0:23:37.05,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,Energy Charge!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.83,0:23:39.71,Default,Title,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Episode 9 \NTurning White and Turning Red
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.05,0:23:38.51,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,Meat Red!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.51,0:23:39.73,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want curry.
